column5: Talk about SCHOOLING  Well done.  I am not sure if that spot is where I am thinking, if so,it has changed some what from the early 80,s .
You’re not missing out on anything over here.  I wish I fished your tribs.
Its amazing how hard they smash the hardware. well done !
Thanks guys 👍 it’s a great indicator when you know the fish are very aggressive.  I’ve had days when they wouldn’t hit a lure and would only take offerings under a float.
Take it you just customized a black/gold rapala. Looks awesome. I do it often to my hardbaits too. Also like the spiral wrap rod you're running

I wish I was talented to customize my own baits but this was bought like that.  I wish I had a few more because I already lost 1 to a steelhead I bought this spiral wrap last fall and I’m liking it a lot.  I still gotta learn how to fight fish with a baitcaster, I find the drag not as smooth as a spinning reel.
